{
  "stem": "17426.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name is Schweickert, was Schweickert.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "S-C-H-W-E-I-K-E-R-T.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can only describe him as being [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] unavailable to any Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anything that he wanted he [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] ordered the Judenrat to function in his behalf.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Judenrat-- head of the Judenrat was Mordha Francus, F-R-A-N-C-U-S.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mordha Francus I knew very well, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was one of the Jews that lived in Dobra and friend of-- well, not my friend, but certainly a friend of my father and my family.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Conditions of the ghetto were extremely difficult.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were restricted, and we were concentrated in a area of about a quarter of a mile square.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every morning, the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] army came in to take Jews to labor for them, to wash, to clean, to clean the horses, to do all kinds of labor.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then another group came in-- the arbeitskommando for us to go out and work on the roads.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Many times I was sitting on my knees and breaking stones into smaller-- approximately two to three inches size-- squares, which they used to fill the road in and build roads with.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were at this point preparing for an onslaught on the Soviet Union, the so-called Barbarossa project.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was early-- this was sort of early in 1941.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we were to do that work for them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say about 300 to 400.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were fewer every day because every night there was something, and every day was something, in which one or two or three or four lost their life in some bizarre ways, unexplained.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Young girls, young men, old men-- it didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just the whim of the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was not even the SS.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
